            <dl class="work-show pt-3 article"  itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
    
<dt>Creator</dt>
<dd><ul class="tabular">
<li itemprop="creator" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" class="attribute attribute-creator_display">
<span>Williams, Ishmael</span><ul><li>Other Affiliation: Epidemiology and Surveillance Branch, Division for Heart Disease and Stroke Prevention, National Center for Chronic Disease Prevention and Health Promotion, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention</li></ul>
</li>
<li itemprop="creator" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" class="attribute attribute-creator_display">
